{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/8527", "repo": "rails", "body": "I think I'd not show the full message (ie with the attribute in it) when the errors are near the fields, I'd rather show `can't be blank` instead of `Name can't be blank`, because it's already near the Name field. For that we already have `errors.messages => {:name=>[\"can't be blank\"]}`.\r\n\r\nIn any case, lets wait for more feedback. If it goes in, it'll need tests and a changelog entry. Thanks for your contribution.", "_id": {"$oid": "523d84c4bd354364b9007731"}, "issue_id": 8527, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/11417790", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/8527#issuecomment-11417790", "updated_at": "2012-12-16T13:43:54Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva", "login": "carlosantoniodasilva", "gravatar_id": "77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837", "html_url": "https://github.com/carlosantoniodasilva", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F60b997fd68261ce70cadaf6c8226c042.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 26328, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2012-12-16T13:43:54Z", "id": 11417790, "owner": "ra